s it right, likely because of mastery.\n", "exercise_id: 3208\nexercise content: 习题\nThe time complexity of building a complete binary heap of size n by the Floyd build-heap algorithm is:Floyd建堆算法建立规模为n的完全二叉堆的时间复杂度为：\n'A': 'O(nlgn)', 'B': 'O(n)', 'C': 'O(lgn)', 'D': 'O(1)'\nknowledge concepts: ['时间复杂度', '完全二叉堆'], is_correct: right\nExplaination: 1. The new exercise contains knowledge concepts: ['节点删除', '二叉搜索树'].\n\n2. Similar to question 3094, there is a direct connection between the previous knowledge points and questions, as both involve 二叉搜索树 and related traversal/search algorithms. The current question extends to 节点删除, which is a natural progression within the topic of 二叉搜索树.\n\n3. Student's Knowledge state:\n树的遍历算法, good; 二叉搜索树, good; 节点删除, good.\n\n4. The student gets it right, likely because of mastery.\n"]

