ficient insertion高效的插入', 'B': 'More efficient deletion高效的删除', 'C': 'More efficient mergence高效的合并', 'D': 'More efficient search高效的查找'\nknowledge concepts: ['左式堆'], is_correct: right\nExplaination: 1. knowledge concepts: ['内存容量']\n\nThe new exercise contains 内存容量.\n\n2. Similar to question 3254. There is a direct connection between the previous knowledge points and questions, as both involve the concepts of 快速排序 and 轴点. However, the current question involves 内存容量, which is a different knowledge point from the previous exercise.\n\n3. Student's Knowledge state:\n快速排序, bad; 轴点, bad; 内存容量, good.\n\n4. The student gets it wrong, likely because of incorrect mastery. Given that the student previously answered questions involving 快速排序 and 轴点 incorrectly, it suggests a lack of solid understanding of those concepts. Although the current question involves a different knowledge point (内存容量) which the student has mastered, the question content and student's answer indicate confusion or incorrect mastery related to the knowledge points involved.\n", "exercise_id: 3208\nexercise content: 习题\nThe time complexity of building a complete binary heap of size n by the Floyd build-heap algorithm is:Floyd建堆算法建立规模为n的完全二叉堆的时间复杂度为：\n'A': 'O(nlgn)', 'B': 'O(n)', 'C': 'O(lgn)', 'D': 'O(1)'\nknowledge concepts: ['时间复杂度', '完全二叉堆'], is_correct: right\nExplaination: 1. knowledge concepts: ['左式堆']\n\nThe new exercise contains 左式堆.\n\n2. It's a new question, there is no direct connection between the previous knowledge points (快速排序, 轴点, 内存容量) and this question's knowledge point (左式堆).\n\n3. Student's Knowledge state:\n快速排序, bad; 轴点, bad; 内存容量, good; 左式堆, unknown/fair (new knowledge point)\n\n4. The student gets it wrong, likely because of incorrect mastery. Although the student has mastered 内存容量, the current question involves a new knowledge point (左式堆) which the student has not demonstrated mastery of before. This suggests a lack of solid understanding of 左式堆 rather than carelessness or guessing.\n"]

